headline: Constant Hype at the TikTok Mansion
abstract: The city is home to a land rush of “collab houses,” where the content creators are getting younger and younger.
lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES — Hype House, the physical location of a new content creator collective, is a Spanish-style mansion perched at the top of a hill on a gated street in Los Angeles. It has a palatial backyard, a pool and enormous kitchen, dining and living quarters.
